======================= ABOUT ========================

Version - v1.0 alpha
Platform - UNIX Platforms (Linux, Mac OS X ...)

FlightGear Requirements -
	> FG v2.10+ (v2.12 recommended)
	> Must support xmlHTTPrequest fgcommand
	> Must support canvas properties
	
xmlHTTPrequest and canvas have been included in FG2.10
and future developments.

====================== INSTALL =======================

Move Contents (gui and Nasal folders) into your $FGDATA
directory and merge the folders.

===================== CHANGELOG ======================

08172013 > Split into windows and unix versions
08172013 > Merlion Menu added with nasal
08162013 > Initial alpha test version

